{"tid":111940,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"香港近年最好導演係邊個？","createTime":"2017-02-07T18:01:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-12T09:50:34.000Z","uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4f3c11806d7aa2354b6848d19746143eca265eb4","tid":111940,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T18:01:16.000Z","msg":"王大導就聽得多<br />\n除左佢仲有邊位係香港同國際影壇都佔有一席位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfdc8838db86738c82f0b6665d190b29ac71f90d","tid":111940,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T18:02:14.000Z","msg":"王晶"},{"pid":"5f65bd79a9fa1983bd4ce108828c44688859c003","tid":111940,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T18:08:59.000Z","msg":"黃修平既狂舞派同哪一天我們會飛都幾正<br />\n前者好熱血柒良又搞笑<br />\n後者個第二男主角幾感動到我<br />\n<br />\n兩套戲以有限既成本黎開戲<br />\n都算係拍出高水準<br />\n<br />\n其實美人魚都幾正<br />\n題材新鮮、多笑位又講環保<br />\n但永遠拍喜劇都被忽視實力<br />\n根本林允D表情就係周星馳現場教佢做一次先<br />\n所以睇林允既表情就好似見番以前既星爺咁<br />\n星爺係一個教戲叻既導演<br />\n如果對方都係有喜感既話"},{"pid":"1d09f3c112237effcd80c5a8a10a42bc0bfcc384","tid":111940,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T18:10:34.000Z","msg":"許鞍華"},{"pid":"69ce42ed67721387b9729b8deee3b3f13e1afc70","tid":111940,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T18:11:15.000Z","msg":"杜琪峯"},{"pid":"2c93988e52b2c2177d36b525fafb09c71f26f0d3","tid":111940,"uid":37901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T20:45:12.000Z","msg":"陳可辛"},{"pid":"6a84e6d62380baba78e521e3ac874f778ffa825e","tid":111940,"uid":53800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T20:45:20.000Z","msg":"梁振英"},{"pid":"333756fa752ba41e63663a6664fee42ce48b9381","tid":111940,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T20:59:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>杜琪峯</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b50282c8ff7cd545348dc88c94d3e7ae935d9e9","tid":111940,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T21:30:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>梁振英</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b020f700ba8affeffc480dced6119cb8b0617e22","tid":111940,"uid":59639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T21:35:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黃修平既狂舞派同哪一天我們會飛都幾正<br />\n前者好熱血柒良又搞笑<br />\n後者個第二男主角幾感動到我<br />\n<br />\n兩套戲以有限既成本黎開戲<br />\n都算係拍出高水準<br />\n<br />\n其實美人魚都幾正<br />\n題材新鮮、多笑位又講環保<br />\n但永遠拍喜劇都被忽視實力<br />\n根本林允D表情就係周星馳現場教佢做一次先<br />\n所以睇林允既表情就好似見番以前既星爺咁<br />\n星爺係一個教戲叻既導演<br />\n如果對方都係有喜感既話</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n美人魚講環保係好<br />\n但成套野用返晒所有舊橋<br />\n食老本都算<br />\n仲要改晒大陸口味 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3279f014623cc49a4ea52b14c3991e9b94cbc17","tid":111940,"uid":3369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T01:18:21.000Z","msg":"杜Sir啦，真正既全能導演，<br />\n拍喜劇愛情劇懸疑片都得，<br />\n仲要有強烈既個人風格"},{"pid":"4b7437ec42c64befa28affa31ef201036a82ff96","tid":111940,"uid":18940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T01:31:26.000Z","msg":"曾國祥都唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n七月與安生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85a22f06cbb800180cfae1533e9f5c416e78d215","tid":111940,"uid":60588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T01:36:59.000Z","msg":"許鞍華"},{"pid":"d980cd0a402fffa1085067134601ec31ad000f91","tid":111940,"uid":11185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T12:26:36.000Z","msg":"許鞍華"},{"pid":"fda9c13356fca5508a85cdf1d0d43c5445d65138","tid":111940,"uid":83713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T13:33:23.000Z","msg":"葉念琛"},{"pid":"07a4c16951ecac2098323cd233ed444275198cff","tid":111940,"uid":74009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T13:35:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黃修平既狂舞派同哪一天我們會飛都幾正<br />\n前者好熱血柒良又搞笑<br />\n後者個第二男主角幾感動到我<br />\n<br />\n兩套戲以有限既成本黎開戲<br />\n都算係拍出高水準<br />\n<br />\n其實美人魚都幾正<br />\n題材新鮮、多笑位又講環保<br />\n但永遠拍喜劇都被忽視實力<br />\n根本林允D表情就係周星馳現場教佢做一次先<br />\n所以睇林允既表情就好似見番以前既星爺咁<br />\n星爺係一個教戲叻既導演<br />\n如果對方都係有喜感既話</blockquote><br />\n黃修平 好撚差"},{"pid":"4bc2213241e171bc1a9c429ac5f25d6a2455324f","tid":111940,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T14:12:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>葉念琛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係旺角活地阿倫"},{"pid":"4746bc15ab20ec0cf6249a736a1d253b39ebba8d","tid":111940,"uid":31054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T14:18:14.000Z","msg":"火火"},{"pid":"eb5810b6f8b2994729b9468b73fb2792840a4030","tid":111940,"uid":12152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T14:20:56.000Z","msg":"杜sir都叫近期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個斷層好大下"},{"pid":"84d7180e9496a3062b4788c094e4244b7c17a795","tid":111940,"uid":7772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T17:08:46.000Z","msg":"juno 套殭屍都唔差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dd1429c9f132417de037ccf61cde226034a38cb","tid":111940,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T17:22:25.000Z","msg":"爾冬陞"},{"pid":"435008b5901f009ded208a1f07ec66f8875fbc12","tid":111940,"uid":71526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T17:41:24.000Z","msg":"李力持"},{"pid":"1cd803a4f9ed64ffdc53416d66c8831808a9e2ce","tid":111940,"uid":38601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T06:07:33.000Z","msg":"翁子光 踏血尋梅<br />\n黃進 一念無明"},{"pid":"6781f53b25d667e66960e79db2b1efd62a552e70","tid":111940,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T09:50:34.000